      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-factory-activity-falls-slow-pmi-shows-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三的一项私营部门调查显示，随着产出和新订单下降放缓，日本四月份工厂活动萎缩速度放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-factory-activity-falls-slow-pmi-shows-2024-05-01/</guid>
